  "texts": [
    "Based on those sizes, the following scores for LoS were assigned:• 360°: is a rendered 360° environment.",
    "For instance, the virtual reconstruction of the \"Villa con ingreso a protiro\" in Italy in the 2nd c. AD [126].",
    "The LoD is a computer science concept that defines the degree of abstraction of a real object versus its virtual representation [142].",
    "As the level of abstraction decreases, the model object appears more realistic.",
    "In this review, the LoD score was based on both its geometrical and radiometrical fidelity."
